,"len()","make([]int,","middletraversal(nod","middletraversal(node.left)","middletraversal(node.right)","movezeroes(num","newstack()","nil","nil{","node","nums，编写一个函数将所有","pop()","pretraversal(nod","pretraversal(node.left)","pretraversal(node.right)","pretraversalnorecursion(nod","push(el","result","return","right","stack","stack)","stack.pop()","stack.push(node)","stack.push(v.left)","stack.push(v.right)","stack.stack.back()","stack.stack.len()","stack.stack.pushback(element)","stack.stack.remove(e)","stack{","stack{stack:list.new()}","struct","tcp","treenod","true","type","v","v.left","v.right","v.val)","val","{","}","三次握手","中序遍历：","为了建立一条可靠的通信信道，客户端和服务端通过三次握手的方式来初始化连接。","二叉树节点定义","二叉树遍历","分布式系统设计","分析","初始状态","前序遍历：","后序遍历","尽量减少操作次数。","必须在原数组上操作，不能拷贝额外的数组。","操作系统与网络","数据结构与算法","数组","栈定义","树","由于","示例","移动到数组的末尾，同时保持非零元素的相对顺序。","系统设计","系统设计与实现","给定一个数组","要提供可靠的通信机制，在传输数据之前，必须先初始化一条客户端（请求端）到服务器（被请求端）的","解答","计算机网络","说明","输入:","输出:","连接创建前","连接建立","连接通道进行数据传输。","连接，在连接正式建立后，双方经","递归写法","非递归写法","题目描述"],"pipeline":["stopWordFilter","stemmer"]},"store":{"./":{"url":"./","title":"Introduction","keywords":"","body":""},"algorithm/":{"url":"algorithm/","title":"数据结构与算法","keywords":"","body":"二叉树节点定义\ntype TreeNode struct {\n    Val   int\n    Left  *TreeNode\n    Right *TreeNode\n}\n\n栈定义\ntype Stack struct {\n    stack *list.List\n}\n\nfunc NewStack() Stack{\n    return Stack{stack:list.New()}\n}\n\nfunc (stack Stack) Push(element interface{}){\n    stack.stack.PushBack(element)\n}\n\nfunc (stack Stack) Pop() interface{}{\n    e := stack.stack.Back()\n    if e == nil {\n        return nil\n    }\n    stack.stack.Remove(e)\n    return e\n}\n\nfunc (stack Stack) Len() int {\n    return stack.stack.Len()\n}\n\nfunc (stack Stack) Empty() bool{\n    if stack.stack.Len() > 0 {\n        return false\n    }\n    return true\n}\n\n"},"algorithm/树/":{"url":"algorithm/树/","title":"树","keywords":"","body":"树\n"},"algorithm/树/二叉树遍历.html":{"url":"algorithm/树/二叉树遍历.html","title":"二叉树遍历","keywords":"","body":"前序遍历：\n递归写法\nfunc PreTraversal(node *TreeNode) {\n    if node == nil {\n        return\n    }\n    fmt.Print(node.Val)\n    PreTraversal(node.Left)\n    PreTraversal(node.Right)\n}\n\n非递归写法\nfunc PreTraversalNoRecursion(node *TreeNode) {\n    if node == nil {\n        return\n    }\n    stack := NewStack()\n    result := make([]int, 0)\n    stack.Push(node)\n    for !stack.Empty() {\n        e := stack.Pop()\n        v := e.(*TreeNode)\n        result = append(result, v.Val)\n        if v.Right != nil{\n            stack.Push(v.Right)\n        }\n        if v.Left != nil{\n            stack.Push(v.Left)\n        }\n    }\n    fmt.Println(result)\n}\n\n中序遍历：\nfunc MiddleTraversal(node *TreeNode) {\n    if node == nil {\n        return\n    }\n    MiddleTraversal(node.Left)\n    fmt.Print(node.Val)\n    MiddleTraversal(node.Right)\n}\n\n后序遍历\nfunc AfterTraversal(node *TreeNode) {\n    if node == nil {\n        return\n    }\n    AfterTraversal(node.Left)\n    AfterTraversal(node.Right)\n    fmt.Print(node.Val)\n}\n\n"},"algorithm/数组/":{"url":"algorithm/数组/","title":"数组","keywords":"","body":""},"algorithm/数组/283.移动零.html":{"url":"algorithm/数组/283.移动零.html","title":"283.移动零","keywords":"","body":"题目描述\n给定一个数组 nums，编写一个函数将所有 0 移动到数组的末尾，同时保持非零元素的相对顺序。\n示例\n输入: [0,1,0,3,12]\n输出: [1,3,12,0,0]\n说明\n\n必须在原数组上操作，不能拷贝额外的数组。\n尽量减少操作次数。\n\n分析\n解答\nfunc moveZeroes(nums []int)  {\n\n}\n\n"},"os_network/":{"url":"os_network/","title":"操作系统与网络","keywords":"","body":""},"os_network/network/":{"url":"os_network/network/","title":"计算机网络","keywords":"","body":""},"os_network/network/tcp_connect.html":{"url":"os_network/network/tcp_connect.html","title":"TCP","keywords":"","body":"连接建立\n由于 TCP 要提供可靠的通信机制，在传输数据之前，必须先初始化一条客户端（请求端）到服务器（被请求端）的 TCP 连接，在连接正式建立后，双方经 TCP 连接通道进行数据传输。\n三次握手\n为了建立一条可靠的通信信道，客户端和服务端通过三次握手的方式来初始化连接。\n初始状态\n连接创建前\n\n"},"system_design/":{"url":"system_design/","title":"系统设计与实现","keywords":"","body":"系统设计\n"},"golang/":{"url":"golang/","title":"Golang底层实现","keywords":"","body":""},"distributed/":{"url":"distributed/","title":"分布式系统设计","keywords":"","body":""}}}